[[Image:DN-SC-87-05770.JPEG|thumb|250px|[[800 Naval Air Squadron|800 NAS]] [[BAE Sea Harrier|Sea Harrier FRS1]] in low-visibility paint scheme.]]

This is a list of the units, aircraft and casualties of the  [[United Kingdom|British]] '''air services in the [[Falklands War]]'''. The numbers in bold are the number of aircraft used in the war, the numbers in brackets are the number of lost aircraft. For a list of air forces from Argentina, see [[Argentine air forces in the Falklands War]].

== Units ==

===Army Air Corps===

* [[No. 656 Squadron Army Air Corps]] - ([[Westland Gazelle|Gazelle AH.1]], [[Westland Scout|Scout AH.1]]) '''6 (1), 6'''

===Royal Marines===

* [[847 Naval Air Squadron|3 CDO Brigade Air Squadron]] - ([[Westland Gazelle|Gazelle AH.1]], [[Westland Scout|Scout AH.1]]) '''9 (2), 6 (1)'''

